request.description: Pesquisa os itens em determinada fila de integração. Necessário requisitar o endpoint DequeueQueueItems para remover os itens da fila após consumo.

Endpoint utilizado para consumir os dados do pedido.

_**PaymentStatus**_: Can be `67 - Cancelled`, `68 - Due`, `73 - Collect`, `79 - OverPaid`, `80 - Paid`, `82 - Refunded`, `84 - PartiallyPaid`, `85 - OverRefunded` or `88 - NotApplicable`

_**ShipmentStatus**_: Can be `68 - Delivered`, `80 - PartiallyShipped`, `83 - Shipped`, `85 - Undeliverable`, `87 - Waiting` or `88 - NotApplicable`  
_**CustomerType**_: 'P' - Person / 'C' - Company / 'G' - Guest  
_**AddressType**_: Can be `66 - Billing`, `68 - Delivery` or `82 - Return`

_**PaymentType:**_ Can be `1 - CreditCard`, `2 - MoneyTransfer`, `3 - PaymentSlip`, `4 - Custom`, `5 - System`, `6 - DebitCard`, `7 - Financing`, `8 - Wallet`, `9 - Deposit`, `10 - Transparent`, `11 - PlaceHolder`, `12 - Offline`, `13 - External`, `14 - GroupPayment`, `15 - LoyaltyCard`, `17 - CustomCard`, `18 - GenericExternal` or `19 - Pix`

_**OrderStatusID**_: Request SearchOrderStatus for more information
